opqry:info.title: Onset Inventory
opqry:info.opqry:message:
# Onset Inventory Generate an inventory of onsets found in both IPA Target and IPA Actual for the selected sessions. Singleton and complex onsets are printed in separate tables with options for generating additional tables for onsets in stressed or unstressed syllables.
## Output Output table(s) will have four columns:
* *Session*
Session name
* *Onset*
Onset
* *IPA Target Total*
Number of occurrences found in IPA Target
* *IPA Actual Total*
Number of occurrences found in IPA Actual
## Example:
Session|Onset|IPA Target Total|IPA Actual Total :---:|:---:|:---:|:---: Anne.Session|p|2|1 Anne.Session|b|1|0 Anne.Session|t|2|0 Anne.Session|d|0|1 Anne.Session|v|1|0 Anne.Session||1|0 Anne.Session|s|2|0 Anne.Session|z|0|1 Anne.Session|h|1|0 Anne.Session|n|0|1 Anne.Session|l|1|0
